# oxlint's default ignore file (eslintignore format). Entries here prune the
# directory walk itself, which is the only thing that keeps oxlint's nested
# config discovery out of vendored trees — .repos/ ships its own .oxlintrc.json
# referencing plugins we don't install, and discovery runs before the
# ignorePatterns in .oxlintrc.json are applied.
.repos/
